<plot>Greta Scacchi, plays a lonely spinster Julia Parchant living on her own on a secluded farm in the mid-west of the USA. Unable to keep the farm by herself she hires a drifter Caleb Tucker, played by actor Bill Sage as her handyman in return for food and lodging. As Christmas approaches the relationship between the two blossoms with surprising and unexpected turn.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?563354</url></doc>
